rows.title: MYSTIC MARTIAL ARTS CYOA
rows.titleText:
Orignal CYOA Creator: /u/L_Circe
Adapted by: goodworld using https://intcyoacreator.onrender.com/

rows.title: INTRODUCTION
rows.titleText: You were curious when you spotted the old, wooden sliding doors, set in between a pair of modern looking buildings. You decided to just peek inside, stepping in as your eyes adjusted, not expecting the doors to suddenly snap shut behind you. To those walking on the street, the doors seemed to open a moment later, but the you that emerged was much different from the you that entered.

objects.title: Gifted
objects.text:
You have no memory of how you trained to gain the power and techniques that you have. You only have the knowledge of how to perform them.

You Have 50 Points
You will gain double points from the Oath Paths shown below, save for Fated Death. You may polish your usage of the powers you have gained, but you cannot improve them or develop new ones.

objects.title: Guided
objects.text:
You have fragmentary memories of your time within the strange dojo. These memories are focused on how to train to improve your powers.

You Have 30 Points
You have the ability to improve upon the powers that you have gained, progressing techniques into stances, and stances into auras. It will take months to years of training to do the former, and years to decades to do the later.

objects.title: Earned
objects.text:
You have crystal clear memories of your time within the strange dojo. You have experienced them in full and real-time, and know not only how to improve your powers, but the processes to acquire new ones.

You Have 16 Points
You can only take one Oath Path from each row. You can improve like you were guided, but at an accelerated pace. You are also able to develop entirely new techniques to train and improve. Techniques in elements you already have experience with will take a year or so. Unknown elements can take longer.

Whichever path you walked, a few things are true. Your body is now at and beyond the very peak of human fitness, passing into feats of mythical prowess, and you know that it will remain such for centuries to come. You, as the saying goes, "know kung fu". More specifically, you know a form of martial arts perfectly suited to your build and temperament. Armed or unarmed, punches, kicks, blocks, it is a style that may be close to a real-life style, or something that is unique.

However, the art you now know is not merely mundane. To start with, you have the ability to create a 'battle aura', a cloak of energy and fighting spirit which can empower your blows and blunt those of others. This aura is powered by both your stamina and willpower, rising when they are high, and fading when they run out. Your style also incorporates several mystical techniques, stances, and additional auras which you will select below. Depending on which path you have walked, it may or may not be possible for you to develop these techniques later. So, choose carefully.

But, first, there are Oath Paths for you to choose from.

rows.title: OATH PATHS
rows.titleText:
You may choose any number of these oaths to uphold if you selected Gifted or Guided above.

You may only choose one oath from each row if you selected Earned above.

If you fail to uphold them, you will lose access to techniques purchased with the points gained.

objects.title: Be Healthy
objects.text: For 3 years, you must live healthily in terms of diet, regular exercise, and refraining from unhealthy habits such as drinking or smoking.

objects.title: Bear The Mark
objects.text: For 3 years, you must visibly wear clothing that has a specific mark on it whenever you fight. You emerged with one such article of clothing, and can make more.

objects.title: Wandering Warrior
objects.text: For 3 years, you must remain on the move, never staying in a given area, such as a city, for longer than 1 month, and not returning to an area you've left for at least 1 year.

objects.title: Fight For A Cause
objects.text: For 3 years, you must fight for a specific cause, such as defending the weak or earning wealth. While you can fight for other purposes, you cannot avoid a fight for this cause, or fight for an opposing purpose.

objects.title: Touch Them Not
objects.text: For 10 years, you must refrain from fighting people belonging to a specific category, which must encompass at least 20% of the population.

objects.title: Teachers Glory
objects.text: Within 10 years, you must establish a school, succeeding in teaching at least 10 students basic martial arts and at least one mystic technique.

objects.title: Life Or Death
objects.text: For 10 years, you must hold to either always preserving the lives of those you fight with, or always killing your opponents in battle

objects.title: In The Know
objects.text: For 10 years, you must refrain from revealing your status as a user of mystic martial arts to any non-martial artist. Prospective students are an exception.

objects.title: Vengeful Rival
objects.text: You had a rival in mystic martial arts within the dojo, who felt humiliated by you. They will have emerged somewhere else in the world at the same time you did, and they have sworn to seek you out and slay you in battle to prove their superiority. They will have a comparable base level of power to you. Decisively defeating them will fulfill this Oath Path.

objects.title: Fated Death
objects.text: You are now fated to only live a mortal lifespan of at most eighty or so years, and then you will face a climactic and satisfying final death in battle. This death is inevitable, and cannot be avoided, resurrected from, survived after, or otherwise negated by any means.

objects.title: Mythic Tournament
objects.text: There is a periodic tournament every seven years, of magic users and mystic martial artists from around the globe and parallel worlds. You must seek out and compete in each of these tournaments, until you win the tournament, and then successfully defend your title as champion at least twice. You will only fail this path if you fail to attend a tournament.

rows.title: Choose your mystic art
rows.titleText:
The first row of powers in each 'school' are Techniques, and cost 1 point.
The second row of powers are Stances, and cost 2 points.
The third row of powers are Auras, and cost 4 points.
Techniques generally allow you to perform a specific attack or ability. 
Stances involve a set of interconnected movements that can have multiple applications.
Auras feature alternative methods of manifesting and using your 'battle aura'. 
You can select powers from any combination of schools that you wish. 
Powers may synergize in unique ways.

objects.title: Burning Fist
objects.text: You can focus heat into your fists (or other striking areas of your body), temporarily causing them to ignite and cause burns on contact.

objects.title: Ash Exhale
objects.text: You can gather fiery energy into your lungs, and expel it as a billowing cloud of burning ash and smoke.

objects.title: Focus Jet
objects.text: You can gather energy to the tips of your fingers, and push it out as a jet of flame. Mentally draining to hold for prolonged periods.

objects.title: Thermal Gaze
objects.text: You can focus energy into your eyes, temporarily overlaying your vision with patterns of heat and cold.

objects.title: Heater Palm
objects.text: You can project a stream of thermal energy from your open palm. This energy will slowly build in a targeted solid object, heating it up over time.

objects.title: Heat Haze Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that build a cloak of highly heated air around you, causing visual distortions and illusions to surround you. Careful use can even turn you near-invisible, and proximity can exhaust your foes.

objects.title: Flare Dash Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that build rings of flame around your wrists and ankles. These rings of flame can be stoked to allow for sudden bursts of rocket propulsion, as well as attacks, and you have techniques for dealing with sudden acceleration.

objects.title: Inner Furnace Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to build up an internal flame, raising your temperature while granting a significant boost to physical strength and musculature. Can easily lead to berserker rages if overused.

objects.title: Dragon Wing Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that engulf your arms in wings of fire, and which can propel wide waves and streams of flame from those wings. Flames can be solid enough to cause physical knockback.

objects.title: Heat Haze Stance
objects.text: Your battle aura can manifest as burning white flames which radiate and flare up on your body. These flames can use energy to burn away wounds, in both yourself and those you come in contact with.

objects.title: Sun God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can manifest in the form of a shining sphere of flame, which will typically hover directly behind you. This sphere generates tremendous heat, and can release burning beams at foes.

objects.title: Strike Nova Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be infused with explosive energy, and shrinks to fit tightly across your body. Every strike can release an explosion upon contact, and this energy can be focused into spheres that can be fired at distant targets.

objects.title: Bubble Fist
objects.text: You can surround your fists (or other striking surfaces) in bubbles, slightly decreasing damage dealt, while strongly increasing the knockback when the bubble pops.

objects.title: Aqua Breathing
objects.text: You can swallow a lungful of water, and use your internal energy to extract oxygen from it, before expelling it.

objects.title: Sharktooth Strike
objects.text: You can gather water around a hand or foot, and then unleash it in a compressed dart. The dart has a sharp edge, and can fly for several meters before losing cohesion.

objects.title: Splash Step
objects.text: You can gather a compressed layer of water under your feet. This layer can be 'detonated' for a boost to jump height, used to absorb fall impact, or can allow for walking on water.

objects.title: Trident Thrust
objects.text: You can gather water and twist it around a limb to form a piercing drill. This drill can extend past your limb for a foot or so.

objects.title: Flowing Current Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that cause streams of flowing water to coalesce around your limbs. These streams can be used to deflect attacks and forcibly puppet your own body to perform impossible dodges.

objects.title: Wave Rider Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that imitate the surging forces of the tides. When used on water or a wet surface, the water can be gathered into a moving mass that can be 'surfed' on to carry you forward.

objects.title: Rain Flicker Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that center on quick flickering movements that border on teleportation. Designed to allow a user to dance between raindrops without getting wet, it is excellent for dodging projectile attacks.

objects.title: Blood Drinker Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allow you to link your blood with that of a struck target, draining vitality from them and into you with each blow. Actually shedding blood will strengthen the effect.

objects.title: Tidal Flow Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can manifest as a spectral liquid flowing around you, surging back and forth with every motion, dragging those caught in it to and fro, allowing you to redirect and counter attacks

objects.title: Deep God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can coat the ground, manifesting as a layer of water several feet across that is like a puddle for you, and a deep lake for others, causing them to fall in while it is manifested and giving you a great deal of water to work with.

objects.title: Waterfall Cutter Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be tightly focused into thin, cutting streams. Typically outlining your body and cutting away at attacks, they can be shot forward in tight jets to cut things at a distance.

objects.title: Pressure Fist
objects.text: You can compress air around your fist (or other striking surface) to unleash a long distance blow. Travels for several meters before dissipating.

objects.title: Sky Edge
objects.text: You can gather wind into a cutting edge along a limb, with the blade extending a few inches beyond your limb as you swing it.

objects.title: Recovering Breath
objects.text: You can take a deep breath, pulling power from the air to replenish your stamina. Repeated use becomes less effective until actual rest is taken.

objects.title: Gale Wall
objects.text: You can gesture and briefly create a sheet of solidified air in front of you, effectively making a wall of wind pushing away from you, which can stop weak attacks and slow others.

objects.title: Feinting Breeze
objects.text: You can stir winds around your body to drag at an attack as you throw it, allowing you to change angles or push or pull blows in unexpected ways

objects.title: Whirlwind Spiral Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that builds twisting whips of wind around your limbs, which can be pushed out to drill at foes, or can loop around objects to pull them towards you or you to them.

objects.title: Dancing Feather Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that can drastically reduce your apparent weight while retaining inertia, allowing you to dance across blades of grass and make tremendous swooping leaps through the air, without weakening the force of your strikes.

objects.title: Vacuum Sphere Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that pulls air from a spherical area between your arms, creating an area of pure vacuum. This sphere can be moved around you, and 'popped' to create a shockwave or piercing line of wind.

objects.title: Gale Runner Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that builds up a tailwind around you, which can be ridden to drastically increase running speed, as well as increasing the speed of your blows.

objects.title: Tornado Eye Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be manifested as a spiraling shell of high-speed wind, circling around you in a tight dome. With focus, cutting blades of air can be shot out from this barrier.

objects.title: Sky God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can reduce the weight of objects within it, including yourself, which can allow for increases in speed as well as true flight.

objects.title: Ill Wind Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can manifest as streamers of foul air, which can suffocate those who try to breath them, as well as lowering the strength of limbs wrapped in them.

objects.title: Stone Fist
objects.text: You can infuse your fists (or other striking areas of your body) with earthen energy, allowing it to strike with greater weight and shielding you against impact.

objects.title: Pebble Shot
objects.text: You can focus energy to summon a small handheld stone, which can be shot like from a sling. Ordinary stones picked up off the ground can also be shot, for less energy

objects.title: Pocket Sand
objects.text: You can summon a handful of sand, which can be thrown and loosely controlled to blind an opponent, and will swirl to abrade their skin.

objects.title: Marble Block
objects.text: You can unleash a pulse of earthen energy at the moment when you block an attack, robbing the attack of much of its force as the energy acts like a solid shield.

objects.title: Crystal Spear
objects.text: You can coat a limb in crystal, which can form sharp points and edges, but is too brittle to be effective armor. The crystal will turn to dust when removed.

objects.title: Diamond Skin Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that sets you in place and thickens and hardens your skin. The longer that you stay in place, performing the motions, the deeper the defenses will sink in, and the longer they will linger when the stance is ended.

objects.title: Stone Carver Stance
objects.text: A set of motions for striking solid objects, gaining insight into weak points and fracture lines within them, and then injecting energy into them to break them along those discovered lines. Works better the harder and more solid the target is.

objects.title: Earth Folding Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to cause the earth under your feet or stone surfaces around you to mold and reshape. The earth can't float or defy gravity, but it can be bunched up to form walls or ramps.

objects.title: Shattering Cliff Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that coats your limbs and torso with a thin layer of stone and rock, which shatters with each motion to barrage targets with sharpened stone shrapnel. Can be used to crack as a reaction to a physical attack, countering with a barrage of gravel.

objects.title: Stone Clone Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be separated from you and infused in nearby earth and stone, creating a puppet you can control. It has your physical abilities, but is somewhat slower, and slows further the farther it gets from you, and is harder to control when you are moving as well.

objects.title: Mountain God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be infused with immense gravity and weight, pressing down on those within range, and adding the weight to your physical movements. You can deliberately exclude some targets with focus, as well as focusing it further on specific targets.

objects.title: Prism Edge Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be manifested as a spectral crystal around you, which redirects moving objects that enter within, especially direct projectiles. Has only a limited resistance to direct force.

objects.title: Thorn Fist
objects.text: You can grow sharp needles from your fists (or other striking surfaces) which are very sharp, but also painless to break off.

objects.title: Sun Eater Sutra
objects.text: You can spread your arms skyward, drawing in energy from sunlight, substituting for food and water as well as restoring a bit of stamina.

objects.title: Swirling Leaves
objects.text: You can summon a flurry of sharpened leaves that fly forward randomly. Accuracy lowers the more leaves that are summoned at once.

objects.title: Swaying Reed
objects.text: You can temporarily empower your bones and joints to be extra flexible, allowing you to dodge and sway around attacks.

objects.title: Sudden Growth
objects.text: You can infuse a burst of energy in the ground with a stomp, causing a plant such as a spear of bamboo or short bush to suddenly burst from the ground. The grown plant will die off in a day or so.

objects.title: Lashing Vine Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that cause flexible vines to grow around your limbs. They can provide support for your limbs, as well as extending out for use as whips or grapples.

objects.title: Deep Root Stance
objects.text: A set of upper-body motions that cause energy roots to sink from your legs into the ground, drawing up energy to sustain your stamina, as well granting you energy to fuel some healing.

objects.title: Bitter Bark Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that coats your body in rough bark, highly increasing your defense. This bark can be shifted and grown into spikes, plates, and other shapes.

objects.title: Blooming Lotus Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allow you to gather natural energy into a small glowing 'seed' between your hands. This energy can then be released as a powerful beam, or as a burst of healing energy.

objects.title: Canopy Brushing Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be pulled inwards into your body, causing you to temporarily grow in size, growing up to double your height with a commensurate increase in strength and mass. This can be tiring to maintain for long periods.

objects.title: Meadow God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura carries the scent of wildflowers, lowering the fighting spirits and soothing the emotions of those in the area. This effect can be shifted to affect certain targets more strongly.

objects.title: Life Nectar Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura takes on the consistency of liquid honey, and is heavily infused with life energy, healing your wounds or those of others. This can be forcibly condensed further, creating an actual physical liquid with healing properties.

objects.title: Wild Fist
objects.text: You can shift your hands and feet into claws or hooves, for additional slashing or striking power.

objects.title: Phantom Tail
objects.text: You can alter your center of gravity as if you had a tail, allowing you to stand and shift in ways that should normally cause you to fall over.

objects.title: Tracking Hound
objects.text: Your sense of smell is greatly enhanced, allowing you to pick up many small details. This effect can be muffled to prevent yourself from being overwhelmed.

objects.title: Horseshoe Kick
objects.text: You can gather energy into your legs before unleashing it in a monstrously powerful kick or jump, which can knock a target even farther than the already large impact should suggest.

objects.title: Venom Stinger
objects.text: You can focus a toxic energy into the tips of your fingers, causing temporary paralysis or illness with a mere jab.

objects.title: Spreading Wing Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allow your arms to act like wings, both in allowing you to strike with sweeping waves of air, and to leap and soar through the air with rudimentary flight.

objects.title: Striking Snake Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that increase the fluidity and flexibility of your body, and which includes knowledge of pressure points to disable targets and accurate strikes to hit them.

objects.title: Clever Ape Stance
objects.text: A set of subconscious motions that allow you to mimic the motions of others as you observe them. Continued observation allows for more accurate mimicry, and even prediction of motions before they occur.

objects.title: Tortoise Testudo Stance
objects.text: A set of motions in preparation before standing immobile, which hardens you against most damage. Breaking the stance can lead to momentary disorientation, but with practice can allow for a powerful counter attack.

objects.title: Bearzerker Fury Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be pulled within, shifting you into a bestial form, with your muscles swelling while hair grows longer. In this form, your strength rises greatly along with your rage, and it can be easy to lose yourself if you are not careful.

objects.title: Totem God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura takes the form of semi-solid animals, which can lash out and attack at your command. Better understanding of an animal will make their 'totem' image stronger.

objects.title: Pack Bond Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be split to infuse a target animal, granting it a large boost in strength and human-level intelligence. The longer you maintain the connection, the more the boost will linger. The target will be loyal to you for as long as the bond lasts, and positively disposed afterwards.

objects.title: Spectral Fist
objects.text: You can wrap your fists (or other striking surfaces) in hazy energy, which allows them to strike at the spirit rather than the flesh.

objects.title: Plague Breath
objects.text: You can gather a foul energy within your lungs and expel it as a noxious cloud. The energy gathered this way won't harm you.

objects.title: Dread Howl
objects.text: You can unleash a chilling howl that carries with it a fearful energy that can cause foes to lock up with terror.

objects.title: Spirits Eye
objects.text: You have a form of second sight that allows you to see spirits and souls, along with a bit of insight to interpret what you see.

objects.title: Vile Nail
objects.text: You can coat your nails in toxins, with even scratches causing nausea and pain. Deeper wounds can cause worse effects.

objects.title: Coiling Threat Stance
objects.text: A set of motions which builds a thin black aura around you, increasing the menace, fear, and dread that your foes feel. This effect is strengthened when actual contact is made.

objects.title: Wraith Wrath Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allows your body to briefly flicker into intangibility. This effect can be focused to just limbs, lasts for only a few moments, and causes numbness and chills in bodies that pass through you.

objects.title: Grave Grappling
objects.text: A set of motions based on grappling and holding an opponent. The tighter and more immobilized they are, the more life energy that you can siphon from them and into yourself.

objects.title: Corroding Claw
objects.text: A set of motions that builds a mist of dark acids around your arms, which burn and corrode away at anything that comes in contact with them. They can be reshaped to an extent to form claws or short blades.

objects.title: Spirit Mantle Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can act as a beacon for spirits of the dead, especially dead fighters and martial artists. Those who heed its call can act as advisors for you, slowly transferring portions of their knowledge to you while they remain near your aura.

objects.title: Assassin God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be tightly focused into the form of a pitch-black weapon, such as a dagger or handclaw. When in this shape, it is extremely difficult to detect, rendering you less interesting to those who can sense such things, while the weapon itself is highly necrotic when used.

objects.title: Crypt Curse Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura is infused with a curse of death, sapping the life energy from those within it. This effect strengthens when you set a taboo, some action such as "do not hit another" that applies to everyone in the aura, including you. Those who break the taboo will have their energy drain faster.

objects.title: Haloed Fist
objects.text: You can surround your fists (or other striking surfaces) with a ring of glowing light. This ring can be detonated on impact, and will have a strong effect when you are morally opposed to your target.

objects.title: Monks Discipline
objects.text: You can sit and meditate to reduce your body's need for food and water. This won't replenish your energy or stamina like actually eating, but it will slow your metabolism to a mere crawl while you meditate.

objects.title: Pure Heart Eye
objects.text: You can focus energy to your eyes, allowing you to see the auras of individuals. Auras will glow with emotions, and will be marred by moral weaknesses or turpitude.

objects.title: Blind Flash
objects.text: With a sharp motion, you can produce a quick and blinding flash of light. This flash can be created on your skin, or within a few feet of you.

objects.title: Beacon Palm
objects.text: You can focus energy, causing your palm to glow with a warm light. This light will naturally draw the attention of those who see it, and introduce a desire to approach.

objects.title: Paladins Hammer Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to surround your limbs in translucent blocks of light. These blocks can both function as armor to weaken blows, and drastically increase the effective weight of physical blows.

objects.title: Angel Feather Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that summons floating feathers of light around you over time. These feathers can be swirled around limbs to lighten them for acrobatics and large leaps, or combined together and used up to form and throw large slashes of light.

objects.title: Heavens Healing Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to build up a cone of light, shining down on you or a target within arm's reach, which drastically increases you or the target's rate of healing. Violent actions by the user or target can disrupt this effect, requiring several seconds to reestablish.

objects.title: Sun Spear Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to focus ambient light into the form of small, handheld spears. The spears are sharp, and have a physical density similar to wood. They can be thrown, but will dissipate several seconds after leaving the user's hand.

objects.title: Law Chain Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be manifested in the form of numerous binding chains of light, which can be extended from you to nearby targets. The chains can be infused with a rule, becoming strong when you uphold the rule or the target tries to break it.

objects.title: Vengeance God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be infused with a judging energy, which causes those within to burn the more 'sinful' or morally corrupt they are. This can be instead inverted, and cause those who are more virtuous to burn.

objects.title: Soul Scale Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be infused with power, generating an opposing force against attacks within it that are fueled by hatred or direct desire to harm, with the force increasing based on the strength of the driving emotion.

objects.title: Spark Fist
objects.text: You can coat your fists (or other striking surfaces) in crackling lightning, which can cause sharp shocks on impact.

objects.title: Static Cling
objects.text: You can emit strong electric fields around your hands and feet, which can allow you to temporarily cling to walls or ceilings.

objects.title: Lightning Nerve
objects.text: You can channel energy to supercharge your nerves, granting a large boost in reaction time. Heightens sensations and results in some pain while active.

objects.title: Energy Surge
objects.text: You can push energy into someone, acting to give them a temporary boost in stamina and vitality.

objects.title: Taser Shot
objects.text: You can focus energy into a small sphere of electricity, which can be thrown and cause temporary paralysis on contact.

objects.title: Magnet Palm Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to charge both hands with polarized energy. Strikes will charge a target with energy, and then the same hand can pull them and the opposite will push them. The opposite fist will also result in a stronger strike while replacing the energy.

objects.title: Bolt Rush Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to charge your legs with energy, vastly increasing jumping, kicking, and running speed. The stance also improves your sense of balance, allowing for acrobatics such as wall-running.

objects.title: Crackling Chain Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to create a network of crackling bolts of lightning around your body. These bolts can act like ropes and chains, and be used to tether you to your foe or the environment, shocking them in the process.

objects.title: Plasma Edge Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to build sheathes of burning energy around your limbs, granting them cutting edges. The sheer heat can sap your strength if used for prolonged periods.

objects.title: Storm Pillar Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura agitates the air above you, generating electric shocks from the sky. Over time, the bolts grow stronger, and they can be somewhat guided when generated via focus.

objects.title: Lightning God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be turned inwards, building up a charge within your body. You can  then release it by transforming into a lightning bolt to teleport over a moderate distance, and even strike at a foe in the process.

objects.title: Grounding Rod Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be tied into the ground beneath you, holding you in place, while allowing you to redirect energy from attacks that enter your aura into the ground instead of you.

objects.title: Chilled Fist
objects.text: You can wrap your fists (and other striking surfaces) in a cold aura that saps heat and energy from those struck.

objects.title: Shuriken Flake
objects.text: You can create handheld disks, shurikens, and daggers out of ice. Crafted items are sharp, but brittle, and will melt rather quickly.

objects.title: Icy Gaze
objects.text: You can focus your gaze on a specific target, causing them to freeze as their movement is impaired and temperature lowers.

objects.title: Slick Slide
objects.text: You can shift your feet to cause ice to appear underfoot, allowing for quick sliding movement. You can always maintain balance on icy surfaces.

objects.title: Icicle Stomp
objects.text: You can unleash a powerful stomp that causes crystals of ice to spring up in front of you. They can either rise vertically or shoot forward diagonally.

objects.title: Gellid Air Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that thickens the air around you, making strikes and movement nearby slower, aside from your own, and lowering the temperature as well.

objects.title: Arctic Armor Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that coats your body in layers of frost to form armor, sapping heat from things that strike it. Slightly decreases your agility.

objects.title: Frozen Mind Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that focuses your mind, locking away emotions while increasing processing and planning speed, and aids in increased economy of motion.

objects.title: Tundra Fog Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that generate thick clouds of fog around you, obscuring your movements and lowers the temperature of whatever is caught within.

objects.title: Aurora Ribbon Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be manifested as ribbons of arctic light, which are loosely controlled by your movements. These ribbons cause whatever they intersect with to flash freeze, which can act like a blade depending on the substance.

objects.title: Winter God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura lowers the nearby temperature and generates a great deal of airborne snow. This snow can be directed, allowing for obscured vision or physical blockades.

objects.title: Frosted Mirror Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be manifested as a reflective haze in the air, which can be focused to create full mirrors that can reflect mystical or energy based techniques back towards their source. Even when unfocused, it can disrupt or distort such techniques.

objects.title: Vibrating Fist
objects.text: You can cause your fists (and other striking surfaces) to vibrate, increasing the damage of strikes as well as causing lingering numbness.

objects.title: Locating Hum
objects.text: You can release a hum that echoes through the area, allowing you to echolocate your surroundings.

objects.title: Power Shout
objects.text: You can release a loud shout that grants a very quick burst of strength and speed.

objects.title: Thunder Palm
objects.text: You can focus energy in your palm (or on a flat part of your body), and then release a blow that generates a loud shockwave through the air.

objects.title: Cacophony Shot
objects.text: You can gather ambient noise into a compressed sphere that can be launched and detonated in a burst of pure sound

objects.title: Bellowing Roar Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that builds up a roaring sound around you as you move. This roar can induce fear, and pushes targets away from you as it grows stronger.

objects.title: Rhythmic Beat Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that consists of simple blows and strikes, which grow stronger the longer you maintain a steady beat and rhythm to them.

objects.title: Silk Tone Stance
objects.text: A set of subtle motions which generate a low, subharmonic noise as you move, which confuses those nearby and can make them more suggestible.

objects.title: Delayed Echo Stance
objects.text: A set of motions which separate the noise of your strikes from their motion, causing blows to land silently, and then a copy of the blow to land a few seconds later, this time accompanied by the noise of the strike.

objects.title: Crescendo Dance Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be filled with a faint music that builds as your movements match it. The power of your body increases as the music builds to crescendos.

objects.title: Silent God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura suppresses all sound in the area, and makes physical movement of others harder. A great aid to stealth.

objects.title: Shattering Reverb Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be injected into targets as you strike them, generating escalating vibrations over time. These vibrations can slowly shake the target apart, but will dissipate when you cease attacking or move away from the target.

objects.title: Unseen Fist
objects.text: You can wrap your fists (or other striking surfaces) in thin shadows, which make it difficult for foes to visually focus on them when you attack.

objects.title: Inverted Gaze
objects.text: You can infuse your eyes with shadows, causing darkness to function like bright light to you and vice versa.

objects.title: Crescent Kick
objects.text: You can infuse your foot in lunar energy, and release an energy blade from a sweeping kick. The blade is stronger in darkness.

objects.title: Midnight Cloud
objects.text: You can summon a large temporary burst of 'smoke', which impairs sight but doesn't affect breathing.

objects.title: Ninja Cloak
objects.text: You can pull shadows around you when motionless, rendering it harder to see you when in dark spaces.

objects.title: Distorted Darkness Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that build a layer of shadows on your body. These shadows can be twisted to temporarily alter the shape of your body underneath to form things like claws or a tail. You will remain generally humanoid.

objects.title: Belted Black Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that cause bands of shadow to wrap around your limbs. The darker your surroundings are, the stronger the blows from wrapped limbs will be.

objects.title: Umbral Cutter Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to create a shadowy outline along your arms. This outline can 'cut' darkness, temporarily brightening an area when you cut through it, and can transfer some damage to a target when you cut their shadow.

objects.title: Shadow Puppet Stance
objects.text: A set of motions to tie your shadow to a target's, forcing them to mirror your actions or you to mirror theirs.

objects.title: Night Curtain Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be infused with darkness, vastly decreasing the light level in your vicinity, and having a moderate muffling effect on other senses of those within it.

objects.title: Lunar God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be manifested into a glowing silvery sphere which hovers behind you, which emits beams of 'black light'. These beams disturb the mental state of those hit by them, causing them to act irrationally.

objects.title: Constellation Beast Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be manifested as points of light linked by lines, which form the skeleton of a large shadowy beast. You are physically weakened while the beast is manifested, but it is very durable, requiring at least half the points be shattered before it will dissipate.

objects.title: Iron Fist
objects.text: You can coat your fists (and other striking surfaces) in a temporary sheathe of metal, adding weight and protection to your strikes.

objects.title: Hidden Sheathe
objects.text: You can conceal a set of weapons on your person, rendering them unfindable until you draw them out. Requires clothes.

objects.title: Whetted Edge
objects.text: You can focus your energy to make blades and edges momentarily sharper.

objects.title: Repulse Buckler
objects.text: You can release a pulse of energy from your forearm, which repels nearby metal.

objects.title: Flying Swallow Cut
objects.text: You can generate a shockwave with a weapon that can bash or cut at a distance.

objects.title: Flowing Kata Stance
objects.text: A set of motions designed to chain together in a series of blows with a weapon that shift slightly to better flow around blocks or obstacles.

objects.title: Filled Hand Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allow you to build up a charge, and then use it up to unleash an attack with empty hands that acts like your hands were actually holding some form of weapon. Can include ranged attacks that rely on physical power, such as bows or slings.

objects.title: Dolorous Blow Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that encases a weapon in a faint black aura, which increases the weapon's effective weight on impact while keeping it light while being swung.

objects.title: Ever-Ready Dervish Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allow your body to spin without getting dizzy, rotating almost automatically to face threats, or to build up momentum for powerful strikes.

objects.title: Many-Angled Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can seem to cause the air to crack and split, causing attacks you unleash to appear to divide to hit from multiple angles simultaneously.

objects.title: Forge God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be focused into your weapon, allowing it to be temporarily reshaped or controlled so that you can attack with it in a different way. For example, a spearhead curving like a scythe or a dagger flying in the air around you.

objects.title: Horizon Slash Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be tightly focused along the edge or striking face of a weapon, and then released to tremendously increase the range of the blow.

objects.title: Gilded Fist
objects.text: You can hold a coin to coat your fist (or other striking surfaces) in a golden glow, which increases your blows power based on the value of the coin.

objects.title: Handy Prop
objects.text: Your luck shifts, such that whenever you reach for an object to throw or attack with, something will always appear readily at hand.

objects.title: Coinshot
objects.text: You can infuse a coin with energy, allowing it to be shot forward like from a gun, with the strength of the blow rising with the coin's value.

objects.title: Shiver of Fate
objects.text: You can meditate to awaken a sixth sense that allows you to detect strong shifts in luck or fate.

objects.title: Critical Sight
objects.text: You can perceive weak points in enemies, areas that when struck would cause more damage.

objects.title: Lucky Step Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allows luck to guide you, causing your body to spontaneously shift on occasion to avoid damage or gain a better angle to attack.

objects.title: Wealthy Harvest Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allow for nigh-impossible pickpocketing while striking foes, and which can sometimes cause coins to spontaneously appear in your own pocket when a foe is defeated, depending on the difficulty of the foe themself.

objects.title: Gamblers Might Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that cause your strength to rise or fall at random. The amount of the boost or loss varies as well, with larger shifts being rarer.

objects.title: Compounding Blow Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that restrict your blows, lowering the power of all of your attacks, while gathering a portion of the lost power to be released as part of a singular, powerful blow.

objects.title: Fortunes Bell Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura causes shifts in luck, marked by the faint ringing of a bell, making those attacking you more likely to experience misfortune. These shifts are not controllable by you.

objects.title: Golden God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can cause golden images to appear in your vision, showing steps needed to complete an immediate goal. This technique only provides guidance, actually fulfilling the steps is a matter of skill, and it cannot teach you further mystical techniques.

objects.title: Blood Price Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be used to destroy a valued object to gain energy, which can be used to heal yourself or others.

objects.title: Regal Aura
objects.text: You can coat your fist (or other striking surfaces) with energy, empowering the strength of a strike by how intimidated the target is by you.

objects.title: En Passant
objects.text: You can release a subtle blow when brushing past a target, unleashing a deep cut with no warning intent.

objects.title: Imposing Demeanor
objects.text: You can shift your body to project intimidation on a specific target. This technique can be focused so non-targets do not realize it is being used.

objects.title: Castling Swap
objects.text: You can grab a target, and cause them to instantly swap places with you, either flipping around or maintaining your same relative facing.

objects.title: Straight Joust
objects.text: You can focus energy into one of your arms and your legs, then charge forward with an extremely powerful piercing thrust.

objects.title: Jumping Knight Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allow you to shift and bounce around seemingly at random. These hops and leaps can be fast enough to appear to be short-range teleportation, but attacking in the middle of a leap is difficult.

objects.title: Gate Breaker Stance
objects.text: A set of motions focused on circling motions of the arms, which pull apart the guard of those you strike, and a powerful blow that multiplies in strength when used right after a target's guard is broken

objects.title: Forking Threat Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that sharpens and projects your intent towards the target, causing them to hallucinate that you have launched an intended attack before you do, and often causing them to instinctively react to that threat.

objects.title: Imperial Marching Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that increase the force of your strikes when you move with confidence, with the magnitude of increase rising the longer you move forward without retreating.

objects.title: Queens Champion Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can allow you to build up and release a great deal of linear force within your body, literally hurling yourself in straight lines in any direction. This can allow for increased power behind attacks, or midair dodges.

objects.title: Commanding God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can press down on the minds of those within it, causing those who fear you or subconsciously submit to become more responsive to your orders, often obeying without question if weak-willed enough.techniques.

objects.title: Pawn Promotion Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can be split, and a portion infused within another. The target will gain a tremendous boost in power and some measure of your knowledge of physical combat. This won't grant them mystical powers.

objects.title: Combo Fist
objects.text: You can cause your fist (or other striking surface) to glow, each blow increasing in power the longer you go without taking damage or missing an attack. A few seconds without attacking resets this.

objects.title: Cross Block
objects.text: You can cross your arms to generate a hazy field of energy around them, which can greatly reduce the strength of hits against it. If used exactly before a hit lands, it can completely negate it.

objects.title: Power Pellet
objects.text: You can gather energy into a glowing sphere, which can either be fired out with the force of one of your punches, or launched at an ally to grant them a small boost in stamina.

objects.title: Street Meat
objects.text: You are able to stomach food of any edibility, treating it as if it was a freshly made and nutritious meal.

objects.title: Dodge Roll
objects.text: You can throw yourself into a diving roll, which can have a chance of causing attacks to simply pass through you as you roll.

objects.title: Idle Animation Stance
objects.text: A set of subconscious motions which can allow you to suddenly spring into full battle readiness from any position. Can include subconsciously activating an appropriate skill if needed when combat starts.

objects.title: Button Masher Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that consist of several sets of simplistic attacks or blocks that can be chained together extremely quickly and without much thought into long strings of attacks.

objects.title: Charge Effect Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allow you to charge up energy and then release it as part of an attack. Charged up attacks will be surrounded with a glowing, flame-like aura that can extend their reach.

objects.title: Third Person Stance
objects.text: A set of motions that allows you to move your focus outside of your body without disorientation, allowing your vision and hearing to act like a camera hovering over your shoulder or off to one side of you.

objects.title: Health Bar Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can cause damage you take to be evenly spread across your body, turning crippling blows into mere full body aches that can be worked through and ignored. Also grants general awareness of the physical condition of those within your aura.

objects.title: Commanding God Aura
objects.text: Your battle aura can cause numerous random 'glitches' to occur in the nearby environment, from non-living objects randomly transforming, to individuals suddenly shifting position, to attacks lagging or spontaneously repeating. You do not control the glitches, but can be immune to them.

objects.title: Limit Break
objects.text: Your battle aura can store a charge when you deal or receive damage. Once this charge reaches a specific high limit, it can then be unleashed in a single empowered attack.
